author: alexdma
msg: Added last unit tests for verifying that:
* loading an ontology with no ontology IRI but a version IRI is still possible;
* the loaded ontology will be anonymous but with a non-anonymous public key;
* OWLOntologyID objects with only a version IRI cannot be created at all, so no further checks for bad public keys are required.
